title: 12-year-old accused of killing man with air-pellet gun
text:
ALEXANDRIA, La. (AP) - Alexandria police say a 12-year-old boy has been booked with negligent homicide after an air-gun pellet killed a 29-year-old man.
Police say Courtney Honore of Alexandria was pronounced dead at a hospital after the shooting Friday evening.
The boy's name was not released because he's a juvenile.
The Town Talk ( http://townta.lk/1jICaY1 ) and KALB-TV ( http://bit.ly/1Mk4o7Z ) report that the boy and man were acquainted.
